data.description: Introducing a stunning pool home in Hesperia on the Mesa, close to the freeway. This immaculate property features a large in-ground pool, fully upgraded interior, and a beautifully landscaped front and backyard. The front yard is fenced, offering privacy and charm. Plus a large (23X30) extra deep and extra wide garage, providing ample space for vehicles and storage.   The spacious living room boasts a cozy fireplace and ample natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is adorned with granite countertops throughout, adding a touch of luxury to the home and next to the kitchen is an extra large laundry room. The large master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with its own fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings. The master shower is generously sized, featuring dual shower heads for a spa-like experience, plus a large jetted tub in the master bath. Additionally, a large walk-in closet provides plenty of storage space.   Backyard is fully landscaped for a resort like feel, with a horse shoe pit as well as for those with recreational vehicles, the property offers a side fenced yard, ideal for RV parking. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a peaceful oasis in Hesperia. Solar currently covers current owners electricity usage this could change depending on new owners usage.
